@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="w-75">
	<p class="text-body-privacy">
		This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our commodity exchange app (the "app"). By using the app, you agree to this privacy policy and consent to our processing of your personal information as described herein.
	</p>
	<h4>What information do we collect?</h4>

	<p class="text-body-privacy">
		We collect information that you provide to us when you register for an account, create a profile, trade commodities, or contact us through the app. This may include your name, email address, phone number, username, password, trading preferences, and transaction history.
	</p>
	<p class="text-body-privacy">
		We also collect information that is automatically generated when you use the app, such as your device type, operating system, IP address, browser type, location data, and usage data. We use cookies and similar technologies to collect this information and enhance your user experience.
	</p>
	<h4>How do we use your information?</h4>

	<P class="text-body-privacy">We use your information for the following purposes:</P>
	<ul>
		<Li>To provide you with the app and its features, such as enabling you to trade commodities, view market data, access your account, and communicate with us.</Li>
		<li>To verify your identity, prevent fraud, and ensure compliance with our terms of service and applicable laws and regulations.</li>
		<li>To improve the app and its performance, such as by analyzing user behavior, feedback, and preferences.</li>
		<li>To personalize the app and its content, such as by displaying relevant ads, offers, and recommendations based on your interests and activity.</li>
		<Li>To communicate with you about the app and its updates, promotions, news, and events.</Li>
		<li>To protect our rights, property, and safety and those of our users and third parties.</li>
	</ul>
	<h4>How do we protect your information?</h4>

	<P class="text-body-privacy">We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We use encryption, firewalls, passwords, and other security technologies to safeguard your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.</P>

	<h4>do we share your information?</h4>

	<p class="text-body-privacy">We do not sell or rent your information to third parties for their own marketing purposes. We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:</p>
	<ul>
		<Li>With our affiliates and partners who help us provide the app and its services to you.</Li>
		<li>With our service providers who perform functions on our behalf, such as hosting, analytics, payment processing, advertising, and customer support.</li>
		<li>With other users of the app who you interact with or trade with through the app.</li>
		<li>With regulators, law enforcement agencies, courts, or other authorities when required by law or when necessary to protect our rights or comply with legal obligations.</li>
		<li>With other parties in connection with a merger, acquisition, sale of assets, or other business transaction involving us or our affiliates.</li>
	</ul>
	<h4>What are your choices and rights?</h4>

	<p class="text-body-privacy" You have certain choices and rights regarding your information. You can:</p>
	<ul>
		<Li>Access, update, correct, or delete your information by logging into your account or contacting us.</Li>
		<li>Opt out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the instructions in those emails or contacting us.</li>
		<li>Change your cookie settings or browser preferences to limit or block the use of cookies or similar technologies by us or third parties.</li>
		<Li>Request a copy of your information that we hold or transfer it to another service provider by contacting us.</Li>
		<Li>Object to or restrict our processing of your information for certain purposes by contacting us.</Li>
		<Li>Withdraw your consent to our processing of your information at any time by contacting us.</Li>
	</ul>
	<h4>How do we update this privacy policy?</h4>

	<p class="text-body-privacy">We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. We will notify you of any material changes by posting a notice on the app or sending you an email. Your continued use of the app after such notice constitutes your acceptance of the updated privacy policy.</p>
	<h4>How do you contact us?</h4>

	<p class="text-body-privacy">If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our handling of your information, please contact us at:</p>
